{"tid":1898950,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"誠意推介一位rapper畀咁多位同路人","createTime":"2020-02-26T10:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T08:39:46.000Z","uid":174174,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"31b863b3914614579a6c73462e475555c663553f","tid":1898950,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:08:19.000Z","msg":"佢叫做阿李，李李<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得佢寫嘅歌詞好講到大家嘅心聲，而且有內涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見佢而家都係得7000幾followers，好想幫佢做打手，希望大家可以幫幫手，推佢上神枱，你當做好youtube戰線又好，支持高質本土音樂又好，幫手subscribe, like &amp; share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己呢排都瘋狂係咁loop，希望大家聽完同我一樣解到心中鬱躁，變得熱血沸騰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢屌藍絲、中立沉默撚、高官，係好出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人覺得代表作係呢首《自由》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0YhtHt-8FBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0YhtHt-8FBY&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6Xx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=7a43b05a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0YhtHt-8FBY</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------歌詞------------------------------------<br />\n<em><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n吶喊嘅聲音 傳遍每一個角落<br />\n因為無人甘心  自由被勒索<br />\n權貴一直被放任  欺善怕惡<br />\n越嚟越多人開始喺黑暗裏面醒覺 <br />\n<br />\n制度暴力 不斷分配利益  蠶食無數個十億<br />\n所謂嘅政績 就係盡力 控制群眾嘅意識<br />\n直至社會變成兩種顏色  <br />\n令群眾互相對敵 係極權嘅目的 <br />\n繼續勞役民眾 繼續服從 直到自由無人珍惜 <br />\n變得絕跡  反對嘅聲音不斷被壓迫 <br />\n直至社會剩低一種顏色<br />\n<br />\n一百萬 你無視民眾嘅聲音<br />\n二百萬 憤怒只會繼續升溫<br />\n你拒絕聆聽 拒絕回應 背棄你嘅使命<br />\n眼白白睇住市民放棄生命<br />\n<br />\n你聽得到我們呼叫嗎<br />\n為了以後 萬百天後<br />\n活在真正自由<br />\n<br />\n你看得到我們掙扎嗎<br />\n為了自由 為了自由<br />\n我們不會退後<br />\n<br />\n煙霧瀰漫 子彈飛散 <br />\n瘦弱嘅身驅根本無力招架<br />\n權貴嘅目的 為左咗利益 拒絕改革<br />\n下令穿上盔甲 用棍棒追打<br />\n無數發子彈 無止境追殺 <br />\n黑同白混合 再分唔清忠同奸 當民意全部係垃圾<br />\n將反對聲音鎮壓 全部厄殺<br />\n隱藏真相 拒絕問責<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爭議嘅條例 令民眾重生 <br />\n再一次重新發現 自由嘅純真可貴<br />\n與其被制度箝制 倒不如企出黎 勇敢講出黎嚟<br />\n拒絕再向權貴敬禮 <br />\n<br />\n不斷被壓逼 要我哋跪低<br />\n不斷被壓抑 要我哋瞓低<br />\n仍然無所畏懼 戴上頭盔 繼續示威<br />\n極權之下彰顯人性光輝 <br />\n<br />\n公平 公義 公開 公正  <br />\n自由想公投 由公眾決定<br />\n市民嘅訴求 你拒絕聆聽<br />\n制度保護暴政 印證權貴失去人性 <br />\n<br />\n自由嘅真諦 我哋誓死捍衛<br />\n唔會容許我哋嘅地方變得封閉  <br />\n子彈嘅威力可以打爆頭盔<br />\n但係自由嘅信念會永遠留低<br />\n</div></em><br />\n<br />\n鍾意嘅話，like埋，你會睇到佢係真手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mc.ali.andy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmc.ali.andy%2F&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6Xx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=794630a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mc.ali.andy/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mc.ali.andy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmc.ali.andy%2F&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6Xx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=0154249e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/mc.ali.andy/</a>"},{"pid":"cc5176cbd0c6c3494668af6d0bdae65bb842f585","tid":1898950,"uid":174174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"其實仲有好多值得推介<br />\n大家有啲咩值得推介嘅抗爭音樂，尤其係rapper，都可以放喺度<br />\n我會幫手刷view數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc18ae593a4b0f4ba154dae172d2cf810e67d23","tid":1898950,"uid":20776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:22:12.000Z","msg":"g持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b76634a975d01a4f6911150804a450c7b34ffa","tid":1898950,"uid":80015,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:23:13.000Z","msg":"luna is a bep<br />\nmatt force"},{"pid":"3a94231a0cf2eceab65d8fe7041d89ed5b5f2071","tid":1898950,"uid":80015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:28:44.000Z","msg":"黃色youtube 經濟圈 CLS<br />\nComment<br />\nLike<br />\nShare"},{"pid":"8d82ea885349ba4c44c044bc25d75f7ffa428afb","tid":1898950,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69b76634a975d01a4f6911150804a450c7b34ffa","tid":1898950,"uid":80015,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:23:13.000Z","msg":"luna is a bep<br />\nmatt force"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:31:20.000Z","msg":"正，我係音樂新手，多謝巴打推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLuna呢首正<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M36-cIjX1D8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM36-cIjX1D8&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6Xx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=0e57dc23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M36-cIjX1D8</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>口口聲聲收成期 你耕緊嗰塊地<br />\n霸足幾十年 肯畀返我哋未<br />\n葡萄成熟 你隨手摘幾粒<br />\n拍拍籮柚留低塊爛地 你咁都得</em></div>"},{"pid":"19df6e6068e171c018fb3b8d91d0e36772428c36","tid":1898950,"uid":242538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:32:50.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />首歌幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b805794f5f18c78d241a3ac5dcb0e22aae181024","tid":1898950,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:33:27.000Z","msg":"【請廣傳】「寧願最後徒勞無功 也不選擇無動於衷」去面對立法會選舉！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fdmKiS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fdmKiS</a>"},{"pid":"057748b532f9137dc494393773b5394961728601","tid":1898950,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:12:49.000Z","msg":"好自豪我係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以聽得明啲咁撚正嘅本土粵語音樂"},{"pid":"fbff58a4970a68c3e0ac9e67f641605b66da5863","tid":1898950,"uid":345908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"推推推[/left][/left]